NetMatrix <- biblioNetwork(M, analysis = "co-occurrences", network = "keywords", sep = ";")

# Plot the network
net = networkPlot(NetMatrix,
  normalize="association", 
  weighted=T, 
  n = 20, 
  Title = "Keyword Co-occurrences",
  type = "fruchterman", size=T,
      edgesize = 20,
      labelsize = 0.7)
